Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Martin Luther King day
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xphm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Jan 1986
Three years after it became law, a national holiday to celebrate the civil rights' leader is observed across the US. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less